data.description: Beautiful Ashton Woods home is located in the gated and guarded Copper Ridge Subdivision.  Offers 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, game room and dinning/study.  This 1 story home has an open floor plan with lots of windows off the family, breakfast room and primary bedroom.  Enjoy the private primary suite, primary bath includes a large walk in shower and a relaxing garden tub.  Home sits on a little bit more than an acre with lots of mature trees and feels very secluded perfect for entertaining.  Enjoy the hot tub on the back patio that conveys.
